description:
“Extra's" Renee Bargh caught up with Lady Gaga at the star-studded premiere of "American Horror Story: Hotel," where she gushed about fiancé Taylor Kinney.

Renee also spoke with series creator Ryan Murphy and Gaga's co-stars Sarah Paulson, Kathy Bates, Naomi Campbell, and Matt Bomer.
